<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Privacy Policy</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #2c3e50;
      --accent: #3498db;
      --bg: #f9f9f9;
      --text: #333;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 850px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 2rem;
      background: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }

    h1, h2 {
      color: var(--primary);
    }

    h1 {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    h2 {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent);
      padding-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }

    ul {
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }

    p, li {
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 3rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #777;
      border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding-top: 1rem;
    }

    .disclaimer {
      margin-top: 1rem;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #999;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .container {
        padding: 1rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> [Insert Date]</p>
    <p>We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring your personal data is handled in a secure and responsible manner. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our application, in accordance with applicable laws such as the Personal Information Protection and Electronic Documents Act (PIPEDA) and other relevant privacy regulations.</p>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Name</li>
      <li>Email address</li>
      <li>Facebook Page or Ad Account ID</li>
      <li>Facebook user ID (only with permission)</li>
      <li>Profile picture and public profile information</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Provide and operate the services offered by our app</li>
      <li>Retrieve and analyze Facebook Page, Ads, or Insights data</li>
      <li>Respond to inquiries or technical issues</li>
      <li>Improve the application</li>
      <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Consent</h2>
    <p>By logging in or granting access via Facebook, you consent to the collection and use of your information in accordance with this Privacy Policy. You may revoke access at any time via your Facebook settings.</p>

    <h2>4. Sharing of Information</h2>
    <p>We do not sell, rent, or share your personal data with third parties, except:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>With service providers necessary to run the app</li>
      <li>When required by law</li>
      <li>To protect the rights or safety of our company or users</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
    <p>If our service includes a website, it may use cookies to enhance functionality and user experience. You may disable cookies in your browser settings.</p>

    <h2>6. Data Security</h2>
    <p>We implement appropriate safeguards to protect your data. However, no system is 100% secure.</p>

    <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You may have the right to access, correct, or delete your data, withdraw consent, or file a complaint. Contact us at: <strong>[Your Email]</strong></p>

    <h2>8. Children’s Privacy</h2>
    <p>Our application is not intended for use by children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children.</p>

    <h2>9. Third-Party Links</h2>
    <p>Our service may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for their privacy practices.</p>

    <h2>10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Continued use of the app implies acceptance of the revised policy.</p>

    <footer>
      &copy; [Your Company Name] • This Privacy Policy was last updated on [Insert Date].
      <div class="disclaimer">
        This site is not a part of the Facebook website or Facebook Inc. Additionally, this site is NOT endorsed by Facebook in any way. FACEBOOK is a trademark of FACEBOOK, Inc.
      </div>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
